<title>jạy bdẖbyḥẗ ḥmd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (jạy bdẖbyḥẗ ḥmd .. bạqdmhạ bqlby ạlfrḥạn
 jạyb lḥn fy ạ̹ydy .. wklmẗ bạqdmhạ bạ̹ymạn)2
 (jạy wbạqdm lyk .. mn ạlly fy ạ̹ydk lyk)2
 (yạ wṭn ạlạ̹nsạn .. yạ wṭn ạlạ̹nsạn)2
 ạlqrạr- (ʿlmny ạ̉qdm lyk .. tsbyḥ yrfʿny ạ̹lyk)2
 wạ̉kwn kdẖbyḥẗ ḥmd .. ạ̉nạ byn ạ̹ydyk
 2- (yạlly ạ̹dytny ḥyạtk ḥb .. ạ̉nạ bạhdy ḥyạty ạ̹lyk
 ḥbk sạkn jwẗ ạlqlb .. wqlby sạkn fy ạ̹ydyk)2
 (qlby ygẖny ạ̉kyd .. ṭwl mạ ạlḥb yzyd)2
 (wyzyd ạlạ̹ymạn .. yạ wṭn ạlạ̹nsạn)2
 3-(ạsmk ạ̉ḥly ạ̉sạmy ạldnyạ .. wạ̉ḥly ạ̉sạmy ạlkwn
 mjd lạsm yswʿnạ ạlgẖạly .. wlljnb ạlmṭʿwn)2
 (sẖms ạlạ̉rḍ tgẖyb .. wạlnwr ybqy ṣlyb)2
 (rạyẗ ạlḥq tbạn .. yạ wṭn ạlạ̹nsạn)2
 4- (mlk ạlmjd wạsmk ʿạly .. wfy ạ̹ydyk ạlslṭạn
 ạ̉mm ạlạ̉rḍ wkl sẖʿwbhạ .. wkl mlwkhạ kmạn)2
 (bkrh htsjd lyk .. tkẖḍʿ tḥt ạ̹ydyk)2
 (yạ ṣạḥb ạlslṭạn .. yạ wṭn ạlạ̹nsạn)2</lyrics>
</song>